1ï¸âƒ£ I want to deploy 10 applications at a time. How to do it?
To deploy multiple applications simultaneously, you can use:
âœ… Kubernetes â†’ Deploy 10 applications as separate deployments in a single cluster.
âœ… Docker Compose â†’ Define multiple services in a docker-compose.yml file.
